data.description: Beautiful 4 bedroom family home in the perfect location, close to everything you need! Spacious floor plan, kitchen with granite counters, stainless steel appliances, breakfast bar, GAS range and ample storage!  Stone corner fireplace in living makes the perfect cozy setting, with tons of natural light beaming through the wooden shutters. Large bedrooms, perfect for kids or guests. Master bath Dual sinks, separate shower and soaker tub ! Great backyard NO back neighbors for those summer BBQ's!
